1
00:00:51,359 --> 00:00:53,560
Sheng Yuanzhou, I knew you'd be here.

2
00:00:55,079 --> 00:00:56,119
Just socializing.

3
00:00:56,759 --> 00:00:58,280
I need to make money too, you know.

4
00:00:59,039 --> 00:01:00,600
When you married into the Sheng family,

5
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:01,759
you should've thought it through,

6
00:01:01,759 --> 00:01:03,280
what you were getting yourself into.

7
00:01:04,120 --> 00:01:05,640
Still making excuses, huh?

8
00:01:06,079 --> 00:01:07,079
Did you let it go to your head?

9
00:01:07,439 --> 00:01:08,159
Get out here.

10
00:01:20,879 --> 00:01:22,640
You do this every time. Aren't you tired of it?

11
00:01:22,640 --> 00:01:23,400
Every time, it's the same with you.

12
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:24,359
What do you really want?

13
00:01:24,599 --> 00:01:25,719
Can't you tell?

14
00:01:25,719 --> 00:01:27,000
I'm just having fun.

15
00:01:27,159 --> 00:01:29,680
Sheng Yuanzhou, remember who you are.

16
00:01:30,159 --> 00:01:31,640
You're still my fiancé.

17
00:01:32,159 --> 00:01:32,879
Jiang Lai.

18
00:01:33,359 --> 00:01:35,000
You didn't actually take

19
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:35,920
this thing between us seriously, did you?

20
00:01:36,280 --> 00:01:38,120
It's just a deal between us.

21
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:40,599
All you want is my status,

22
00:01:41,480 --> 00:01:42,760
or the Sheng family's money.

23
00:01:43,319 --> 00:01:44,200
Am I wrong?

24
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:46,000
Zhang Xiaobei.

25
00:01:46,319 --> 00:01:47,959
Do you even remember who you are?

26
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:50,120
But right now, I think

27
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:52,280
being Sheng Yuanzhou, Sheng's eldest son,

28
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:54,239
looking down on everyone every day,

29
00:01:54,599 --> 00:01:56,840
with beauties in my arms, feels damn good.

30
00:01:57,640 --> 00:01:59,840
I wonder who swore so confidently back then

31
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,959
that he'd become Zhang Xiaobei again?

32
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:03,799
That poor home...

33
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:06,760
Those miserable days...

34
00:02:07,519 --> 00:02:08,639
I don't want to go back to that.

35
00:02:09,199 --> 00:02:10,599
Besides, Sheng Shizhong

36
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:13,319
has already acknowledged me as his son.

37
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,280
He knows who I am

38
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:17,280
and still chose to accept me.

39
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:19,800
You think you can still control me?

40
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:21,240
Let's go.

41
00:02:28,199 --> 00:02:28,599
Hello?

42
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:32,400
Yes, we're already staking it out.

43
00:02:33,159 --> 00:02:34,199
Editor-in-Chief,

44
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:37,560
can you stop giving me this kind of job?

45
00:02:37,919 --> 00:02:39,039
I investigated Prosperity Group

46
00:02:39,039 --> 00:02:41,120
to expose their black market transactions.

47
00:02:41,439 --> 00:02:42,039
I'm not trying to look at

48
00:02:42,039 --> 00:02:43,800
some rich kid's gossip news.

49
00:02:44,159 --> 00:02:44,800
I'm telling you,

50
00:02:45,319 --> 00:02:46,759
gossip news is what really grabs

51
00:02:46,759 --> 00:02:47,599
the public's attention.

52
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:49,240
Then we follow the clues.

53
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:56,560
Zhang Xiaobei, this is how you treat me?

54
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:01,879
I already made it clear to you in there.

55
00:03:02,759 --> 00:03:04,360
Let's not waste each other's time.

56
00:03:05,159 --> 00:03:07,439
After all, The night is young.

57
00:03:08,159 --> 00:03:08,800
I'm leaving.

58
00:03:20,159 --> 00:03:20,719
Thanks.

59
00:03:27,199 --> 00:03:28,439
Si Qi.

60
00:03:31,159 --> 00:03:32,479
You're back from the US.

61
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:33,439
Yeah.

62
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:35,080
I've been back a week.

63
00:03:43,319 --> 00:03:43,919
Congrats.

64
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:45,479
Your dream of being a reporter came true.

65
00:03:45,759 --> 00:03:46,319
Yeah.

66
00:03:46,719 --> 00:03:49,039
Everyone's changed this past year.

67
00:03:49,639 --> 00:03:50,360
Speaking of which,

68
00:03:50,919 --> 00:03:52,080
I should thank you guys.

69
00:03:52,719 --> 00:03:55,240
If you hadn't cornered me back then,

70
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:57,159
I wouldn't have had the courage

71
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:58,879
to chase my dream.

72
00:03:59,639 --> 00:04:00,680
Actually, before this,

73
00:04:02,039 --> 00:04:03,280
I really did treat you as a friend.

74
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:06,680
Now

75
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:09,240
I dig up dirt on the rich for a living.

76
00:04:09,759 --> 00:04:11,039
Wanli Construction should be careful too.

77
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:15,479
Sure.

78
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:16,759
You're welcome to talk anytime.

79
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:25,920
A large number of workers

80
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:28,160
gathered outside Baochi Automobile Factory

81
00:04:28,319 --> 00:04:29,199
to protest.

82
00:04:29,199 --> 00:04:31,319
As for Prosperity Group's acquisition,

83
00:04:31,639 --> 00:04:33,959
it's said that if it goes through,

84
00:04:34,519 --> 00:04:36,560
Prosperity Group will enact mass layoffs.

85
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:39,720
Then many workers will be Displaced.

86
00:04:39,959 --> 00:04:40,560
So?

87
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:42,399
Have you decided?

88
00:04:42,519 --> 00:04:43,160
Director Lu.

89
00:04:43,519 --> 00:04:44,360
If you ask me,

90
00:04:44,519 --> 00:04:46,079
these workers' livelihoods

91
00:04:46,839 --> 00:04:48,399
are none of your damn business.

92
00:04:48,879 --> 00:04:49,879
I'll say it again.

93
00:04:50,759 --> 00:04:52,519
The acquisition has only one condition:

94
00:04:52,879 --> 00:04:53,639
No layoffs.

95
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:58,439
Every single worker keeps their job.

96
00:04:59,120 --> 00:05:00,920
Now you're trying to set terms with me?

97
00:05:01,519 --> 00:05:02,360
Take a look around.

98
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:04,000
Right now, besides me,

99
00:05:04,279 --> 00:05:06,480
who'd buy your crappy factory?

100
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:07,920
I suggest you think it through.

101
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,759
Sell it while you still can.

102
00:05:10,319 --> 00:05:12,079
Don't let it rot in your hands.

103
00:05:12,279 --> 00:05:14,000
Until it's just worthless junk.

104
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:16,560
You know our factory's history.

105
00:05:16,959 --> 00:05:19,240
We started as a five-man auto parts shop,

106
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:21,240
and grew into what it is today.

107
00:05:21,519 --> 00:05:23,279
Every worker here is family.

108
00:05:23,279 --> 00:05:24,720
All right, all right, stop, stop.

109
00:05:25,079 --> 00:05:25,800
I'm telling you, Director Lu,

110
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:28,720
all that "one with the workers" stuff,

111
00:05:29,199 --> 00:05:30,399
is fine as a slogan.

112
00:05:30,839 --> 00:05:31,879
If you actually mean it,

113
00:05:32,120 --> 00:05:33,519
then you're being kind of stupid.

114
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:34,160
How about this:

115
00:05:35,839 --> 00:05:36,959
I'll pay out of my own pocket

116
00:05:37,519 --> 00:05:38,240
and give you 200,000.

117
00:05:38,720 --> 00:05:39,120
How's that?

118
00:05:41,079 --> 00:05:41,879
Every man for himself,

119
00:05:42,519 --> 00:05:43,680
as the saying goes.

120
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:48,040
Why are you so stubborn?

121
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:48,920
Let's go, let's go.

122
00:05:49,439 --> 00:05:50,759
Take your money and get the hell out.

123
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:52,800
Don't think everyone's like you people,

124
00:05:52,959 --> 00:05:53,680
mercenary.

125
00:05:53,839 --> 00:05:54,279
Get out!

126
00:05:59,959 --> 00:06:01,800
Their bid is actually twice ours.

127
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:03,480
What's their background?

128
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:04,920
I looked into it.

129
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:06,680
It's an investment firm from Singapore.

130
00:06:07,879 --> 00:06:08,680
Singapore...

131
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:15,319
Looks like I need to meet an old friend.

132
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:28,480
Get to the back of the line.

133
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,519
No Antique appraisal. I need someone.

134
00:06:30,519 --> 00:06:31,759
Even to find someone, get in the back.

135
00:06:32,439 --> 00:06:33,959
We lined up before dawn.

136
00:06:34,519 --> 00:06:35,639
Don't try to pull any tricks.

137
00:06:39,319 --> 00:06:39,759
Next.

138
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:48,199
Didn't think you'd be so hard to see now.

139
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:49,759
What needs an Antique appraisal?

140
00:06:50,879 --> 00:06:53,040
You're doing well under the Long family.

141
00:06:53,439 --> 00:06:54,720
Why come mess with my business?

142
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:56,399
I don't know what you're talking about

143
00:06:56,639 --> 00:06:57,639
The Baochi Automobile Factory thing.

144
00:06:58,800 --> 00:07:00,399
You pulled Lisa into it, didn't you?

145
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,560
I've thought it over and over

146
00:07:03,279 --> 00:07:04,720
The Singapore funds

147
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:07,199
Then it had to be Lisa, no one else

148
00:07:07,399 --> 00:07:10,399
Is Lisa's family the only investor there?

149
00:07:10,519 --> 00:07:12,240
But to go against Prosperity Group,

150
00:07:12,639 --> 00:07:14,000
I'm afraid she's the only one.

151
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:17,920
Your time's almost up

152
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:21,959
I'm telling you

153
00:07:22,399 --> 00:07:23,800
Even if it's Lisa's family

154
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:26,439
They'll never shake Prosperity Group.

155
00:07:31,399 --> 00:07:32,439
Time's up

156
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:35,680
You've changed a lot

157
00:07:36,279 --> 00:07:37,160
Same goes for you

158
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:40,279
Never thought Sheng Yuanzhou

159
00:07:40,439 --> 00:07:42,519
Would ever have the nerve to fight me

160
00:07:44,639 --> 00:07:46,040
So how does Father plan to handle it?

161
00:07:46,639 --> 00:07:48,079
He's got the Long family behind him now

162
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:49,160
So what about the Long family?

163
00:07:49,519 --> 00:07:50,920
Aren't they just antique dealers?

164
00:07:51,199 --> 00:07:52,000
You think I'd be scared of him?

165
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:57,040
I was his father once, remember?

166
00:07:58,399 --> 00:08:00,399
It's time to teach him a lesson

167
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:06,480
Hello?

168
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:08,720
Why do the handoff here?

169
00:08:09,399 --> 00:08:10,879
The goods are in the car

170
00:08:11,519 --> 00:08:12,160
Go ahead and check them

171
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:14,279
You're not sending anyone over?

172
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:22,920
Hello?

173
00:08:23,879 --> 00:08:24,360
Hello?

174
00:08:40,799 --> 00:08:41,600
Si Qi

175
00:08:42,399 --> 00:08:43,440
Zhang Xiaobei

176
00:08:45,919 --> 00:08:46,639
What are you doing here?

177
00:08:48,279 --> 00:08:49,440
I got word that

178
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:51,039
Prosperity Group is smuggling goods here

179
00:08:51,279 --> 00:08:52,240
So I came to check it out

180
00:08:52,919 --> 00:08:53,960
What about you, why are you here?

181
00:08:54,519 --> 00:08:55,519
Prosperity's

182
00:08:57,879 --> 00:08:59,279
I'm doing a pickup for the Long family

183
00:09:01,399 --> 00:09:02,840
What does that have to do with Prosperity?

184
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:06,320
In a place like this

185
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:08,360
Doing a purchase handoff

186
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:10,399
The supplier insisted on meeting here

187
00:09:10,559 --> 00:09:11,519
I think it's strange too

188
00:09:30,759 --> 00:09:31,279
Fakes

189
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:34,799
Something's off

190
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:37,519
Watch out!

191
00:09:53,159 --> 00:09:53,720
Are you okay?

192
00:09:55,279 --> 00:09:56,360
I think I twisted my ankle

193
00:09:59,039 --> 00:09:59,440
Over here

194
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:04,000
Come on

195
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:07,879
Let me see

196
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:09,240
No, no, no, it's fine

197
00:10:09,720 --> 00:10:10,279
Don't be shy about it

198
00:10:10,879 --> 00:10:11,639
I'm long over it

199
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:16,360
It's not too bad

200
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:19,200
Use hot and cold compresses at home.

201
00:10:22,759 --> 00:10:23,320
What are you laughing at?

202
00:10:25,279 --> 00:10:26,399
I just think

203
00:10:27,279 --> 00:10:28,440
It's kind of amazing

204
00:10:28,960 --> 00:10:30,200
A year has passed

205
00:10:30,919 --> 00:10:33,840
It feels like everything changed

206
00:10:36,279 --> 00:10:37,240
And yet nothing did

207
00:10:39,679 --> 00:10:40,519
It's true

208
00:10:43,720 --> 00:10:44,440
Everything changed

209
00:10:46,399 --> 00:10:46,759
Come on

210
00:10:47,559 --> 00:10:48,039
I'll carry you

211
00:10:49,120 --> 00:10:49,600
Uh, well...

212
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:51,480
No, I'm fine, I can walk

213
00:10:51,879 --> 00:10:52,480
Get on

214
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:54,480
You feel like you can stand and walk now

215
00:10:54,639 --> 00:10:56,200
But walking will make your ankle worse

216
00:10:58,679 --> 00:11:00,159
Sheng Yuanzhou, Sheng Yuanzhou!

217
00:11:00,320 --> 00:11:00,960
Sheng Yuanzhou!

218
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:03,919
What are you doing?

219
00:11:05,799 --> 00:11:06,600
Put her down!

220
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:08,360
Why are you here?

221
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:09,720
Someone told me

222
00:11:09,720 --> 00:11:11,200
You ran into danger picking up the goods

223
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:12,399
So I rushed right over

224
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:13,320
And what happened?

225
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:15,039
There wasn't any danger at all

226
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:17,320
This is obviously Cheating.

227
00:11:18,600 --> 00:11:19,840
Lisa, you've got it wrong

228
00:11:20,559 --> 00:11:21,879
Tell me, what did I get wrong?

229
00:11:26,399 --> 00:11:27,440
Do you still like her?

230
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:28,720
Stop it

231
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:29,759
We're just friends

232
00:11:29,759 --> 00:11:30,639
Sheng Yuanzhou

233
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:34,159
I've helped you so much

234
00:11:34,360 --> 00:11:35,279
And this is how you treat me?

235
00:11:35,799 --> 00:11:36,840
You'll regret this

236
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:44,360
With all that's happened today

237
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:46,279
Something's definitely wrong

238
00:11:46,799 --> 00:11:47,639
Then what about her?

239
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:53,240
Mr. Sheng

240
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:56,879
I agree to your terms

241
00:11:57,279 --> 00:11:58,720
I drop my Baochi Automobile Factory bid.
